data.description: This 5 bedroom contemporary home is situated on 2 lots, 1.5 beautiful acres, at the end of a private cul-de-sac, offering peace and tranquility. The large open kitchen is a standout feature with a skylight that floods the space with natural light. Granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a garden bay window make the kitchen a chef's dream. The garden bay window is an ideal spot for growing your own herbs, adding a touch of freshness to your culinary creations.  The great room is impressive with vaulted ceiling and inviting fireplace, creating a cozy and welcoming atmosphere.  Additionally there is a family room with a fireplace, providing ample space for relaxation and entertainment. The landing between the 2 stories offers a unique feature, a perfect spot for growing plants. This creative use of space brings the beauty of nature indoors. At the end of a long day, retreat to the spacious master suite that features vaulted ceilings, plenty of closet space and a balcony where you can enjoy your morning coffee or a glass of wine in the evening. The en-suite bathroom features a jetted tub, where you can soak away the days stresses. The other 3 bedrooms also offer vaulted ceilings, adding to an airy and spacious feel.  The walk-out basement is a versitile space featuring a large rec room with wet bar, perfect for hosting gatherings or enjoying leisure activity, a 5th bedroom and a kitchenette.  Newer windows and flooring throughout most of the home. Call for a showing!
